[10] Brazil (Sao Paulo)
Date: Fri 13 Jul 2007
Source: Jornal da Manha [in Portuguese, trans. & summ. Mod.TY, edited]
<http://www.jornaldamanha.com/visualizar.php?not=19434>

Yesterday [12 Jul 2007], the [Marilia] Municipal Secretary of Health
reported there have been 17 new dengue cases; 16 clinically diagnosed
and one by serology by the Instituto Adolfo Lutz. Although there is
less rain, [virus] transmission continues.
